§ Definition ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ An ❬ellipsoid❭ (or ❬hyperellipse❭ or ❬hyperellipsoid❭) is a
    set $E ⊂ 𝗥^{n}$ for which there exists $A ∈ 𝗥^{n ×n}$
    positive definite satisfying
    ◇ ⦊
      ‖ E = \Set*{x}{\transpose{x}Ax ≤ 1}. ⦉
    ⦉⦉
⦉

